-bhop_vale. 
the reason why its called vale is cause of the artist album Jack Anderton - Vale or valley for short, originally i was gonna map a small valley for this map but as time and mapping passed along optimization got harder for the map the reason why i stuck to 2 stages, now i also didn't really map this after an "artist album" i also wanted to see how beautiful i could make csgo knowing there are some great maps out there but i put my self to the test in detail and lighting. so i did =)
Enjoy!
